sources.description:
PizzaFLIX Marathon Edition! Complete 15-chapter Cliffhanger!
Starring: Ralph Byrd, Irving Pichel, Jennifer Jones (as Phyllis Isley)
Writer: Chester Gould (comic strip by)
Directors:  John English & William Witney
Ralph Byrd stars as the granite-jawed detective, DICK TRACY, who sets to capture master spy Nicholas Zarnoff before he can put his criminal gang back together again!

metadata.Plot: A mad doctor named Zanoff uses a drug to bring himself back from the dead after his execution in prison. Dick Tracy sets out to capture Zanoff before he can put his criminal gang back together again.
metadata.Writer: Barry Shipman, Franklin Adreon, Rex Taylor
metadata.Actors: Ralph Byrd, Irving Pichel, Ted Pearson
